hopobject.body: An envelope provera tablets to induce period This sounds like a really cool invention, but the guy who made the Segway thought it was going to change personal transportation and it never did. How will all the devices communicate with the Nymi? Will we need special locks, a new car, point of sale terminals etc? NFC had similar promises and so far all I've ever used that for is sending a picture once just to try it out.
